Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.47,0:02:10.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:18.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H575F66&\4c&H575F66&\pos(640,504)\blur3\1c&HCCD4DD&}Wolf and Hope and Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I'm looking for someone with a stock of pyrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:30.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you remember what I said about Amarty’s method of making money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:37.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be too pitiable for Amarty if I were to help you too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:44.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I also remember that Deanna dislikes business talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this was going to be business talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to know, no matter what –
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,how to get Deanna to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:59.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you after the alchemists' stockpile?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's so profitable?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:10.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you want to know your future, or heal some illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for my own personal gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:23.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my gain isn't anything related to the soaring value of pyrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...more basic need. {purpose might fit better?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When our cart sinks into mud and won't budge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:37.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we weigh the choices of abandoning it or doing whatever it takes to pull it out on a scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:41.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The value of the goods, the profit, the amount of cash on hand, the travel route,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the cost of paying for someone’s help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:51.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the danger of running into bandits while we're floundering around in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:56.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We take all those kinds of things into account when we're deciding whether to abandon our cargo or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're in that kind of situation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to abandon my cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can load it back onto my cart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how much trouble it causes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:06.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with no time and no other way out, a good merchant will wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say this to big sis:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:14.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've come to buy a crate of white feathers."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely repay—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:25.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be enough if you just share another ancient legend with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:30.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I sound as dignified as big sis just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:10.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me for disturbing you so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:12.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Lawrence. I visited you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize how rude this is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've come to buy a crate of white feathers."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess festivals really do attract people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:45.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite rare for me to have several visitors in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:53.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you came to buy a crate of white feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that from Bartose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:57.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:05.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's the type to give in to mere persistence, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:11.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of business proposal was enough to persuade even that stubborn old mule?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask your permission to buy pyrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:20.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The skyrocketing pyrite that everyone's talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:25.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have some special reason, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:30.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That man wouldn't have helped someone who was simply looking to profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:36.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the pyrite not for business, but to settle a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With my cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:55.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A traveling merchant's enemy is always his cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Weighing its value, planning its handling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and researching where it should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:05.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If he misjudges on any one of these points, a traveling merchant will lose out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:11.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm trying to steady a piece of cargo that's about to fall off my cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:21.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because after rethinking its value, delivery, and destination, I realized I absolutely cannot lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:26.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Buy a crate of white feathers."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such an overblown passphrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:36.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It really just means that you have to entertain me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:40.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A happy bird will drop feathers when it flaps its wings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:45.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who have the passphrase pick and choose who gets to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just pick out the little details of my guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only pyrite you're after, I'll allow you to purchase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:56.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:57.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone has already bought some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How much of it? At what price?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:11.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That customer bought on credit and didn't actually take any goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say they merely placed an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:14.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,On credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:19.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally I wouldn't mind hand it over to you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:24.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount was about 1600 Iredo worth by today's market value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 400 Trenni silver worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:29.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, what's the name of this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:31.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:40.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For safety reasons, we don't reveal the identities of anyone doing business with alchemists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be for something normal since you mentioned a duel, so I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you know the results as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:10:00.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where will I be able to contact you tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:05.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the mineral merchant's stall at the marketplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:10.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be available there throughout the day's trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Money is no object,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as they don't ask for double the market value or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:19.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please inform them that I'm willing to pay quite generously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for barging in on you so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:26.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind if you stayed all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you brought some interesting tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:34.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:36.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:47.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any legends of pagan gods and humans becoming mates?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:57.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're in a hurry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:07.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can discuss those stories later, at your leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:34.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it up with Deanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But someone beat me to it so I'm not sure how it'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat you to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:42.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So... at this point I can only rely on what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll pay in Trenni silver, they'll sell 370 coins worth of py—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you want everyone to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,370 Trenni silver worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about it after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:14.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone like me without much money, it's simply a bit of pocket money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about if I had some real money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:21.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'd be able to hold back in the midst of this racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:26.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I expect there were a lot of people who secretly bought up lots of it on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:34.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're all town merchants with their reputations on the line, not lone traders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:38.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Buying it isn't an issue, but the price rose too much so now they're at a loss as to how to sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:43.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The profit from selling just a small amount is huge, so it stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:48.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who is sensitive of their position would be desperate to sell it off somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:52.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you sent out your apprentice and had him tell them:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:58.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"A traveling merchant blinded by greed says he wants to buy pyrite with cash."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"How about it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:01.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're okay with it I could start negotiations right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, right awa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:18.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This where you're just supposed to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right. Sorr...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:40.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until recently you were a traveling merchant to the core from head to toe and inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:45.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You never truly thought of me as a friend, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But how about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:56.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I still rank as just another convenient merchant to trade with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:05.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people who become town merchants after spending a long time as traveling merchants tend to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But here's something even more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were faced with the possibility of me leaving this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:18.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,would you be running around town this frantically?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:21.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,that's exactly what you're doing for the sake of your companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:31.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You started traveling with that girl out of pure luck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:36.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just accepted the circumstances as they came.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm watching myself when I first met Adelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Poets say love can't be bought with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:50.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Preachers say there are things more important than money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So even though we work so hard just to earn money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:15:00.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,how can we obtain something so much more important than that? {<- lives/posession .. my liberty feel free to tweak.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good one, Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:10.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously we would consider something which took great effort to obtain to be precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:15.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are times when those precious things enter our lives unexpectedly simply.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And though you didn't even realize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you've been protecting your princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:24.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a knight isn't just about physical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, because Amarty is from a good family,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you may have seen him as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the leading actor in this story. {LAWL fourth wall}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can answer that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo, put your tail back inside would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:34.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mark tell you what the plan is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:36.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping you lay a trap for the evil villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go into the details but that's pretty much it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:50.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I might need to ask you to take on a difficult task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Lanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ewell Lanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were born farther north than even here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:01.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:04.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from a village frozen in snow and frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with I'd like a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go buy something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:23.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,One coin is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:26.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one is for your share, little partner. {best I can do to word this. what a weird sentence >_> }
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:30.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll pay you a proper reward later too, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep hanging around, your master's going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd say breakfast is a luxury, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go spoiling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've stopped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cold lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be troublesome if he caught a cold because I let him go hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We both benefited then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, his part in this is important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. {added}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I intend to watch the market until noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it looks like it's rising too much, I'll sell enough pyrite to drop it back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way of knowing what the turn of events will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:20.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible my fate will lie on Lanto's shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how many prospective buyers there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:28.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And zero sellers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This will keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,800 Iredo on average!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 80 times the starting value!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right to hold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How will Lawrence win this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:48.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, do you know how an item's value rises?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:54.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's lot of people who want to buy it compared to the amount that's available.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And how it drops?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:00.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversely, when there's too much of that item.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:02.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:06.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, for a market to heat up, there needs to be a certain amount of sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:12.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If nobody sells then the only ones who profit are the ones who are holding back their stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:19.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The price goes up because there are a certain number of sales and new buyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:26.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, his aim isn't to profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to stop Amarty from profiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:35.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to sell a large amount of pyrite at the perfect time in order to force the price to drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:42.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Amarty sells even 1 second before that and achieves his target of 1000 silver, there's no hope left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:47.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the ability to hold back and to make a determination are needed to time it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:56.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not worth that much yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate it's not going to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The buyers are just increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:07.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How many are there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:09.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:48.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even more people will gather when the market bell chimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:51.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd hand this over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:52.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:54.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The payment as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Lima gold coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared 14 coins at todays opening market rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It may have been presumptuous of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:16.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought it'd be inconvenient for you to carry 300 silver coins around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The service charge for exchanging these must have been costly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I consider it to be merely good manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I acknowledge receipt of the payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wish to count them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:40.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With that done, I'd like to take the contract for the 300 silver now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:52.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Wolf and Trustworthy God
